      <title>Self-Hosted Finance: Taking Control of Your Money with Actual Budget</title>
      <link>https://l4linux.com/portfolio/self-hosted-finance/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 23:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
